Attachments
precis:
Acceptance of an Instrument (REVOCATION OF SURRENDER) wherein the DITIDAHT
BAND OF INDIANS revokes the surrender it made on May 17, 1943, with respect
to the harvesting of the marketable timber on Chuchummisapo Indian Reserve
No. 15 and on Saouk Indian Reserve No. 16, in British Columbia.
